.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, engineer, journalist, manager, musician, photographer
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, brown, amber, apricot, blue, black
 1. the person who likes mauve is the accountant##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is the journalist##1
 3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person who likes brown is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person who likes blue is between the person who likes black and the photographer##2
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who likes brown is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the person who likes mauve is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the person who likes black is the person drinking water##1
15. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
| Job         | analyst    | journalist | accountant | manager | photographer | musician | engineer |
| Color   | aquamarine | apricot       | mauve     | brown | amber   | blue    | black      |

