There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, colombian, french, indian, japanese, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, march, august, april, february, may, november
 1. the malaysian is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the freelancer is the chinese##1
 4. the firefighter is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the australian is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is the doctor##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the australian##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the colombian is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the person who's birthday is in june is the indian##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the australian##1
16. the person who's birthday is in april is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
