 3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person who growslily is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the analyst is the person who growstulip##1
12. the analyst is the person who growstulip##1
13. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
